Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,之前还能编三股辫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,任其摆布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村同学好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,头发扎起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以后就一直这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学帮你扎的吗 好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊 脸那么小
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 打铃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,堀 宫村没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是因为刚才那些女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明明之前还把你当空气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,剪个头发就变脸成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且居然还当着我的面卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们每天摸来摸去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是宫村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我都没认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,亏你能认出来啊 谷原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太没良心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 最近还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见还长高了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,耳洞也太吓人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谷原 你们也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,听你叫名字真是让人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,上了高中飘了吗 有病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你还让柔弱的女孩子帮你拿东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样啦 人家没准是他女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,到手个漂亮妹子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 吭一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,说完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是他女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他初中什么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那叫一个阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,总是一个人 看着都觉得可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你话说完了没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,滚 高中脑残
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那啥 当时我心情不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会对他们那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,发了一下火嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们那样说你坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 薯条和可乐是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谷原 那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你开始玩真人格斗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才碰上宫村了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,初中的时候你经常找他麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,关我屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看着像女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你说堀同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫堀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我劝你还是别像以前一样找他麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他的防御力可今非昔比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 到底是女朋友还是召唤兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,表面上总是说看他不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,心里却还是在意他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 有话就直说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能替我生气的人就在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,巴 巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一巴掌就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那啥 就跟之前一样不要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好不好嘛 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有你这么求人扇巴掌的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她都求你了 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是从哪里冒出来的啊 进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我大老远就看到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还不是被你爱理不理的样子逼出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就你这样也叫男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你还看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道就别插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不就那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,色色的要求呗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没半毛钱关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村已经不喜欢我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么烦恼找我就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说我不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你来也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还说不是色色的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真想敲开的你头看看里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 我们要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再强硬一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 京子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再见进藤 别再给我色了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 宫村 我想去便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,去去去 去他妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是啥情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谷原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,自己买
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,干吗那么凶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,能别在便利店门口扎堆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,召唤兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有种再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们啥情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我们在这儿捡垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,又名回收小队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,险些骨头都被打凹进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啥情况 怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 那不是宫村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 下次再遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村也惹不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,心累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底遭遇了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么play
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,堀 说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就当是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村是不是转型了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,男高十八变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,变成啥样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,初中的时候别说打女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说啥他都不敢顶嘴来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 这就回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,晚饭前要回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,京介你还没走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 京介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事想找你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况 有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啰嗦 这是男人之间的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你想说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要在浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 事情是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟堀同学有关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 咋了咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有第二个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哪来的第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我发火她就会开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啥情况 你们在玩啥play
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,估计那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是单纯喜欢看你反差的反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,反差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你正装打扮上班的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾 差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你就当是收服魔像怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快点出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这样别人还怎么洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,京子 闭上嘴乖乖坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村他都这么烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村他为了满足你可是煞费苦心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这事跟你有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有时间在那儿说闲话不如帮我干点家务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大实话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这话真难听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可爸爸我之前做了咖喱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呀你个头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不就热个速食咖喱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可你当时明明说好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,能不好吃吗 他都给你做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,创太吃了还要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这舒适的温度是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 宫村身上冒热水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快把衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别当着我的面脱啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天放学我和秀一起去卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,英语 不行不行太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,结果那家伙只会唱演歌和RAP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他真是什么歌都听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明明外文歌也听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沟内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,居然不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该喜欢堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,堀到底有多受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在我敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有相当的觉悟会吃苦头的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,话说堀人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,应该在学生会室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 手机不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是换教室的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沟内同学也忘东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你有看到手机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们之后也没有其他人用这个教室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,号码多少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那个090——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不就在你的屁股口袋里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 真的帮大忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,黑屏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了就别弄坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沟内同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢痛揍堀同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,痛 痛揍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这 我没法对她下手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们之间是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,手机找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,透跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是老喜欢放那里才会忘记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了 臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,堀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沟内同学 别管她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你是那种磨磨唧唧的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点小看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你对自己的女朋友一点都不含糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼角好红啊 擦到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 挤死了给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,出去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,外面啊 外面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,话说这是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,「外面」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,「外面」 这里就是「外面」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一自由的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个外面跟鞋柜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的「外面」 就是跟鞋柜一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谷原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是一直在「里面」不懂罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么玩意儿 刚才开始一直扯什么里面外面的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你先开始的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来这还是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能像这样好好对话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢狭窄的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我也讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,「里面」开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,至少比这里开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就算「里面」空无一人也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果「里面」的人都出去了 只留下你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你就只有一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你所在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是「外面」或「里面」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而是「有人」或「没人」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你在意的是有没有伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村的手机号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,知是知道 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和兔子最亲近的人就是宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,兔子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了 快把手机号给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,伊澄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把外面的看板拿进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今天已经打烊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是休息日 后天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,过了前面那个弯直走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有家挺大的蛋糕店 那边应该还没关门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,后天是吧 后天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿的芝士蛋糕很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这样 我后天再来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,水果塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再加这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,各两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,各两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那我再来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 手机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,现在坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要拿去修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 还以为是故意不接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,原来故意的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谷原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记喂它们饲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,明明那天轮到我喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假后那些兔子死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是我把责任推到了你头上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那天 我能对你说出这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在胸口就不会这么痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好 这样就弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,毕业相簿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那是初中的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,初中时期的堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,敢看就弄碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一直头疼放哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大一本放着有点碍事 扔了又可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,已经扔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想过要扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,又沉又大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道该放哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不过终究没扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它对自己而言有多么宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村过去一定有想要抛弃的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不认识初中时期的宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只是猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他有许多不喜欢 想要遗忘的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他终于能坦然面对过去 庆幸未曾抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道片桐的毕业相簿长啥样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道才会期待嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过照片4月就拍好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能和沟内同学合照就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我们关系变好了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还一起找了手机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然之前他一直对我很冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但总有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这人是M吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有谷原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定也和我合得来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然一定很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这世上没有谁是无法成为朋友的
